What is in the box?

    User Guide (PDF)

    From the manufacturer

    Dynamic Bass with Dolby Atmos

    A dynamic bass driver of 10 mm employed in the realme Air 3 Neo Bluetooth Headset delivers outstanding sound, sharp vocals, and reinforced bass. You can also experience exceptional sound quality with Dolby Atmos and hear your favourite song comes to life.

    AI-powered Noise Cancellation

    The AI ENC technology in the realme Air 3 Neo eliminates background noise, ensuring that you are never disturbed by your surroundings. This way, you can take calls and experience flawless communication wherever you are.

    Powerful Battery

    The realme Buds Air 3 Neo, with its robust battery that can last up to 30 hours, keeps you connected and happy all day long, whether you're watching your favourite shows, blasting through your music, or embracing an adventure.

    Lag-free Experience

    With the exquisite audiovisual synchronisation of the realme Buds Air 3 Neo, you can thoroughly immerse yourself in every game. Furthermore, you can easily swap to gaming mode to relish a stutter-free experience.

    Efficient Bluetooth Connectivity

    The Bluetooth 5.2 in this headset offers efficient transmission, strong anti-jamming capabilities, a reliable signal, and low energy consumption, enabling you to appreciate its superior performance.

    Water-proof Build

    Thanks to the IPX5 water-resistant certification, you can take this headset with you to the gym, water sports adventures, and even listen to your favourite songs in the rain.
